@startuml deployment-diagram
title Deployment View — Click to Live Distribution Model
skinparam nodeStyle rectangle
skinparam nodesep 60
skinparam ranksep 80

node "Development Environment" as DEV {
  node "Developer Workstation" as WS {
    artifact "Godot Editor 4.6+\n(Forward Plus Renderer)" as GODOT
    artifact "GDScript Source Code\n(scripts/)" as SRC
    artifact "Blender Assets\n(.blend files)" as BLEND
    artifact "Git Repository" as GIT
  }
}

node "Player Environment" as PE {
  node "Player Machine (Windows)" as PM {
    artifact "Click to Live Executable\n(D3D12 Rendering Driver)" as EXE
    artifact "Godot Runtime (embedded)" as RT
    artifact "Jolt Physics Engine" as JOLT
    artifact "Local Save Data\n(user://)" as SAVE
  }
}

SRC --> EXE : export via Godot\n(Windows preset)
BLEND --> EXE : imported as meshes
EXE --> SAVE : read/write\n(save games, settings)

note right of DEV
  **Development Stack**
  - Godot 4.6.1
  - GDScript
  - Blender for 3D assets
  - Git for version control
end note

note right of PE
  **Runtime Stack**
  - D3D12 rendering driver
  - Jolt Physics for 3D physics
  - Local save data in user://
  - No server required
end note

@enduml
